  B -->|Fail| Bx["Resolve CS timing and pull-up/power faults"]
  C -->|Fail| Cx["Verify I2C address and pull-ups"]
  D -->|Fail| Dx["Verify UART level and baud"]
  E -->|Fail| Ex["Reduce TX power, check legal/antenna/path"]
  F -->|Fail| Fx["Tune input debounce/ISR mapping"]
  H -->|Fail| Hx["Pause and document"]

  Bx --> B
  Cx --> C
  Dx --> D
  Ex --> E
  Fx --> F
  Hx --> G
